########################## REQUIREMENTS ##########################
A word doument with more than 1 bookmarks. The file must not be password proteted.
######################## FIELD INFORMATION ########################
Source Document(Required): Document which is to be split.
Destination Folder(Required): Folder location where the documents to saved after the processing is completed.
FileNames(Required): List of names of file which will be given to resulting documents. Make sure the names are in the same sequence as they appear in the document. Atleast 2 file names are required to start the process. E.g First name is the list will be given to the first file created.
If the source doucment gets split into more documents than the names provided then they will be named as the sequence number of its occurrence. E.g If the source document was split into 4 documents but the FileNames list has only 3 names then the fourth file will be named as 4.docx.
Prefix(Optional): This value will be added to all the resulting documents name as a prefix.
Suffix(Optional): This value will be added to all the resulting documents name as a suffix.
